[src:nushell/commands] Sets a default value if a row's column is missing or null.
[src:nushell/commands] Describe the type and structure of the value(s) piped in.
[src:nushell/commands] Attempt to automatically split text into multiple columns.
[src:nushell/commands] Run a closure, providing it with the pipeline input.
